| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0736 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 78a5812e-eb2e-583b-b9f1-d759270ea2ee"
